  "abstract_short": "First regime-consistency check: EFC with derived μ(a) achieves Δχ²=+1.7 vs ΛCDM across BAO, SN, RSD.",
  "keywords": [
    "EFC",
    "unified analysis",
    "BAO",
    "SN Ia",
    "RSD",
    "μ(a)",
    "entropy field",
    "regime consistency",
    "modified gravity"
